---
// Componente Hero - Sección de introducción
---

<section
    id="hero"
    class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 pt-24 md:pt-20 pb-10"
>
    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-12 w-full">
        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-16"
        >
            <div class="text-center md:text-left order-2 md:order-1 flex-1">
                <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 pb-3 neon-white">
                    <span id="typing-text"></span><span class="typing-cursor"
                        >|</span
                    >
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-3 text-gray-300 font-light">
                    Técnico Superior de Sistemas
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-sm md:text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Actualmente me desempeño como técnico de sistemas tras haber cursado ASIR, pero mi gran objetivo es llegar a especializarme en el sector de la ciberseguridad. Soy un apasionado por la tecnología y me encuentro siempre en constante aprendizaje.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-7 justify-center md:justify-start items-center"
                >

                    <div class="flex gap-7">
                        <a
                            href="https://github.com/DorianSGT"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="social-icon group"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="imagenes/github.png"
                                alt="GitHub"
                                class="w-9 h-9 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 white-icon"
                            />
                        </a>
                        <a
                            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dorian-garc%C3%ADa-a09402350/"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="social-icon group"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="imagenes/linkedin.png"
                                alt="LinkedIn"
                                class="w-9 h-9 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 white-icon"
                            />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-shrink-0 order-1 md:order-2">
                <div
                    class="avatar-container relative w-32 h-32 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden group"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/imagenes/avataar.png"
                        alt="Dorian García"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover block transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    const text = "Hola, soy Dorian García";
    const typingElement = document.getElementById("typing-text");

    if (typingElement) {
        let index = 0;
        const typingSpeed = 100;
        function typeText() {
            if (typingElement && index < text.length) {
                typingElement.textContent += text.charAt(index);
                index++;
                setTimeout(typeText, typingSpeed);
            }
        }
        setTimeout(typeText, 500);
    }
</script>

<style>
    /* CURSOR TYPING */
    .typing-cursor {
        display: inline-block;
        animation: blink 1s infinite;
        margin-left: 2px;
        font-weight: 100;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
        0%,
        50% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        51%,
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }


    /* ICONOS SOCIALES */
    .white-icon {
        filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
        opacity: 0.7;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-icon:hover .white-icon {
        opacity: 1;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px #7dd4fc5f) brightness(0) invert(1);
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* AVATAR */
    .avatar-container {
        border-radius: 50%;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(white, black);
        -webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(white, black);
    }

    .avatar-container::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -150%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(
            to right,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0%,
            rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.6) 50%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%
        );
        transform: skewX(-30deg);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .avatar-container:hover::after {
        animation: sheen 0.8s ease-in-out forwards;
    }

    @keyframes sheen {
        100% {
            left: 150%;
        }
    }
</style>
